Class Student

java.lang.Object
classes.User
classes.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<User>
public class Student extends User
Intranet System's Student model. Represents the student of University. Has his own year of study, degree, faculty and specialty to which he belongs. Can study courses, and Mark represents his academic performance, which is expressed by attestation points and GPA. This class posses the functionality of viewing news and rating teachers of belonging courses.
